videos.description: Jaden Ivey leaves the defender in the dust with a crossover, then steps back for the long 3-pointer.

videos.description: Purdue's Eric Hunter Jr. splashes the 3-pointer, forcing an Indiana timeout and has Purdue Pete doing the Griddy.

videos.description: Indiana guard Xavier Johnson gets into the lane and lobs it up to Trayce Jackson-Davis for the huge flush.
